eption indications for ultrasonography and/or explanation of the doughnut and pseudokidney signs. <em>Pediatr Radiol</em>1985; 15: 388–391.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/BF02388356">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/3903639/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Pediatr+Radiol&amp;publication_year=1985&amp;pages=388&amp;doi=10.1007%2FBF02388356&amp;pmid=3903639">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">15.</div><div id="R15" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content"><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-firstauthor"><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-snm">Gayer</span><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-fnm">G</span></span>, Hertz M, Zissin R. CT findings of intussusception in adults. <em>Semin Ultrasound CT MR</em>2003; 24: 377–386.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S0887-2171(03)00073-8">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14620719/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Semin+Ultrasound+CT+MR&amp;publication_year=2003&amp;pages=377&amp;doi=10.1016%2FS0887-2171%2803%2900073-8&amp;pmid=14620719">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">16.</div><div id="R16" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content"><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-firstauthor"><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-snm">Rintala</span><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-fnm">A</span></span>. The histological appearance of gastrointestinal polyps in the Peutz-Jeghers syndrome. <em>A